Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀨能同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳，做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼都不跟我們說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒有辦法幫妳處理的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12話 天使的微笑\N所有狀況都對妳不利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12話 天使的微笑\N到底發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12話 天使的微笑\N請妳老實地說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們還有辦法處理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙同學，算…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經不是一句算了\N就可以解決的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上已經出現傷患了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，遙同學所看見的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有弄傷瀨能同學的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是當場看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女拿著奇特的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在現場對吧？祐一同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個…什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳還是打算這樣保持沈默
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞的情形\N就只好轉交給校方處理…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能暫時讓我跟修女兩個人\N獨處一會兒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子，請交給我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬排飯送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂上的傷並沒有那麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能是在跌倒時扭到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左側腿骨有裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個比較令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她之所以沒有昨夜的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是因為受傷而造成的\N暫時性打擊引起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要太過擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼能夠對妳說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱那個無依者的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要妨礙妳們的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道這點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又打算怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟對方挑戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事情，我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事情，我怎會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，看到朋友被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被消除記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也無法忍受\N總是這樣被蒙在鼓裡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是無法對妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妳或許會憎恨妳的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我認為，幸好妳是HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很討厭耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是用那種含糊其詞的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們只好自己採取行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，為了某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要藉助妳的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的名字我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，又來跟妳借用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是老樣子\N突然就冒出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩境製藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學園的讚助廠商之一對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在創立祭的時候\N我有見過他們的高層人士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡頭還是沒有西爾斯財團\N以及其相關企業的名字出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留，謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以做太過危險的事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石上…老…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!請放開我!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是獻身給神…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…神…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我或許無法像神一樣\N能完全包容妳的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是相對的，我卻擁有\N可以抱住妳的一雙臂膀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳該休息一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經整整兩天沒睡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!\N不管那個茶飯女做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是也有我的骨氣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強自己喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是雪之!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這個\N我還可以再撐72小時!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真刺激～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，妳去小睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，妳跟我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒睡覺就無法發揮實力對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可要"彎"回名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挽回名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到修女竟然是女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂 「燈塔下是最黑暗的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼們真的做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實燈塔塔底是很黑的哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到教會地底下\N竟然會有這種玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉沙 ．西爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是檯面上的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也沒想到妳竟然會光明正大\N用本名直接殺進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從實招來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底想要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這間學校有何目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是野蠻的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優，收拾她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對抗女武神時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不在對方\N將心之子具像化時加以打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，平常根本不用找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會很帥氣地…登場的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼配合度都這麼低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說無關…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵不是妳的室友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就這麼想裝好人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧也是一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小～碧～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是妳上場表現的時候耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣\N就靠我們自己去拼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼的事情我們會想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你別再插手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你什麼忙也幫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別管我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能不管啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎樣都跟你無關吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你忘記之前發生的所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，沒看到遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之在的話\N那傢伙一定會跟來才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後面跟著的，應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是跟舞衣在一起呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為舞衣煮飯很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟舞衣在一起很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣笑的話，我也會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣要是哭了，我也會難過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命，妳真的很喜歡舞衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡舞衣煮的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他種喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的應該不是飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是舞衣本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔!原來我喜歡舞衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此!原來如此!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣子啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想一定是這樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雪之，我也喜歡妳唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡小命喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙她啊，總是那麼地直接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉著笨拙又膽小的我\N做這個做那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候\N也有被她耍得團團轉的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是對小遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，小命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛安娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣子，我很困擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城同學會有\N遭遇無依者的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是為了小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切靠妳了喔，命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳怎麼突然說這種話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼在沿海的廢工廠那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我同學被抓了，要快!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是麻煩妳…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西爾斯財團？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在歐美大型企業背後的\N神秘資本集團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其權力甚至足以影響\N總理的位子要給誰坐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳更正一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是影響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自遙遠的古代以來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的命運便是由我們來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了迎接即將來臨的黃金時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有艾莉莎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是騙人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學!艾莉莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認艾莉莎．西爾斯的基因情報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以D模式重新啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除4號至12號的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優，加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填鉻彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，妳沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!趁現在，快攻擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的讓人非常感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月社？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個自稱吸血鬼的變態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎也坦承在本校犯案了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…成功了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後只有妳自己一個人\N很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔負了讓教會聲譽受損的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實該受到懲罰的是我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是很傑出的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說，我的計畫太草率了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本委員會卸除你的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事情\N妳一個人辦得到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我創造出來的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動密碼α79
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指令優先順序…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你設置的暗碼已經全部消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優是我重要的朋友耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所聽到的，你被開除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬瑟夫．葛瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後由我來進行指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了迎接下一個黃金時代來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～玉響之夜～\N舞衣學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～玉響之夜～\N要怎麼做才可以那麼大呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～玉響之夜～\N啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～玉響之夜～\N我是認真的!請告訴我!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼說我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保密是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐好小氣!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!不要吝嗇啊!說!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，怎麼連妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙呀，妳記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在就讀幼稚園時\N第一次見面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.99,0:24:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙家還不像現在這樣富有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們常常一邊等爸爸媽媽回家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊在我的房間裡面吃飯對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.17,0:24:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳雖然總是會抱怨\N我的消極態度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.74,0:24:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻還是一直保護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要永遠跟著小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.85,0:24:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙妳總是全力向前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.22,0:24:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了不要被妳拋下\N只能拼命地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.79,0:24:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙還是會回過頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.36,0:24:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我伸出援手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.47,0:24:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊，其實有發現到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.60,0:24:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最溫柔的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.67,0:25:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力追上妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.68,0:25:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能永遠在一起\N那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.05,0:25:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
